    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Medaeops serenei, new species. Holotype male. A, third maxillipeds; B, male abdominal segments 3 – 5, 6 and telson; C, right fourth ambulatory leg; D, left G 1; E, left G 2. Scales A, B = 2.0 mm; C = 5.0 mm; D, E = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/177165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

